  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Focusing in the northern Western fjords, this 7-night holiday combines a stay in the ‘glacier’ resort of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen" title="Loen">Loen</a><span>, home to some of the fjords most spectacular scenery, with the vibrant coastal city of </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a><span>. It is a great option for those who wish to get up close to nature. Located at the end of the Nordfjord, guests can explore the arms of the largest glacier in continental Europe and Loen’s surrounding walking terrain. A contrasting stay in the sunny city of Ålesund allows guests to get out onto the water with a variety of trips at the entrance to the fjords.</span><span></span></p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
