<h2><a name="Tour highlights"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Tour highlights</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Experience the best of Norway's glittering glaciers along the coast</li>
<li>Admire the breath taking views from the brand-new Loen Skylift</li>
<li><span>Optional ‘Troll Car’ buggy ride to glacier</span></li>
<li>Enjoy a relaxing boat cruise to the Seven Sisters waterfall</li>
<li>Visit the seaside town of <span>Ålesund</span></li>
<li>Enjoy sunset views from the top of Mount Alaska</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="hhttps://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Itinerary"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Itinerary</span></h2>
<p><strong>Day 1: UK to Loen</strong></p>
<p>Fly to Ålesund airport where a transfer will be waiting for you to Loen on the Nordfjord (approx. 3½ hrs). </p>
<p>Meals included: Dinner</p>
<p><strong>Day 2: Loen</strong></p>
<p>The first part of your holiday in<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen" title="Loen">Loen</a><span> </span>will be focused around the impressive glacier arms with optional guided excursions to the Kjenndal and Briksdal glaciers, both of which are accessible by foot via a short gentle walk. On the drive, you will pass some of the Nordfjord’s breathtaking scenery including the turquoise waters of Lovatn Lake and the cascading waterfalls of Oldedal valley. At Briksdal, there is also the option of taking a ‘Troll Car’ buggy ride to the glacier (approx. £20 per person). Another ‘must-do’ is a day trip to the Geirangerfjord, stopping at the Dalsnibba viewpoint on the way, for a memorable cruise past the famous Seven Sisters waterfalls. Or venture out by foot around Loen’s surrounding pastures, waterfalls, peaks and new walking trails at the top of the Loen Skylift Cable-Car. </p>
<p>Meals included: Breakfast, Dinner</p>
<p><strong>Day 5 or 4: Loen to Ålesund</strong></p>
<p>Today, you will transfer back to <a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a><span> </span>centre on a stunning drive, ready for your stay in this Art Nouveau city. </p>
<p>Meals included: Breakfast</p>
<p><strong>Day 6 or 5: Ålesund </strong></p>
<p>Ålesund is a bustling port and seaside town, home to some interesting architecture after it was totally rebuilt after fire in 1904 in an Art Nouveau style. Less-visited than other cities in Fjord Norway, it has retained its authenticity and charm. From here, guests have the opportunity to take the ‘Royal Fjord Route’ on a Hjørundfjord cruise, visit the ‘Atlantic Road’ &amp; ‘Trollstigen’ National Tourist routes (pre-bookable round trip by public transport), visit one of the many city museums detailing the area’s fascinating history, or the surrounding islands and skerries including Runde bird island by boat. A trip up to the top of Mount Aksla, reached by bus or 400 steps from the city centre, provides an excellent view over the city and harbour, especially at sunset. </p>
<p>Meals included: Breakfast</p>
<p><strong>Day 8: Ålesund to UK</strong></p>
<p>Return by shuttle to Ålesund airport for your flight back to the UK. </p>
<p>Meals included: Breakfast</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Your holiday includes"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Your holiday includes</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK (supplements may apply)</li>
<li>Scenic transfers from the Ålesund airport to Loen and back to Ålesund centre</li>
<li>Shuttle transfer from Ålesund centre to Ålesund airport</li>
<li>Accommodation with private facilities throughout</li>
<li>Half board meals included in Loen</li>
<li>Bed &amp; Breakfast in Ålesund</li>
<li>'Meet &amp; Greet' service throughout your stay, with a welcome to the resort and 24/7 phone service</li>
</ul>
<p><span></span><strong>Your holiday excludes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Any extras, drinks, gratuities and personal expenses</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h2><a name="Hotels"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Hotels</span></h2>
<p><strong>Standard Hotels</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>★★★+ <a data-udi="umb://document/7780b99803294b0f8a9519ed836b9830" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen/loenfjord-hotel" title="Loenfjord Hotel">Hotel Loenfjord</a>, Loen</strong></li>
<li><strong>★★★+ <a data-udi="umb://document/89e354afa6824ae197da03b9604055e7" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund/first-hotel-atlantica" title="First Hotel Atlantica">First Hotel Atlantica</a>, Ålesund<a data-udi="umb://document/89e354afa6824ae197da03b9604055e7" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund/first-hotel-atlantica" title="First Hotel Atlantica"></a></strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Superior Hotels </strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>★★★★ <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen/alexandra-hotel" title="Alexandra Hotel">Hotel Alexandra</a>, Loen  </strong></li>
<li><strong>★★★★ <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund/hotel-brosundet" title="Hotel Brosundet">Hotel Brosundet</a></strong><strong>, Ålesund </strong></li>
</ul>
<p><em>Monday departures - 4 nights Loen, 3 nights Ålesund</em></p>
<p><em>Friday departures - 3 nights Loen, 4 nights Ålesund</em></p>
<h2><a name="Departure dates"></a><span class="geolocation-title">Departure dates<a></a></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Any Monday or Friday throughout the summer</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-norway/glaciers-coast#Tour highlights">[Back to top]</a></p>]]></description>
